Title: Marathon Man - set
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jryn8
Last Broadcast Date: 14 April 2004
Our correspondent prepares for the London Marathon, the second in a series. BBC Science Correspondent, Richard Black is in training for the London Marathon. Why marathon training doesn't result in significant weight loss - training tips and techniques. There is also the importance of cod liver oil, as a nutritionist explains. Show less